name: Subsidiary Branch Lobby, The Offshore Firm (2021)
description:
"Subsidiary Branch Lobby"
The Offshore Firm (2021)

Metarealistic game photography depicting hypercorporate, antisocial, and liminal virtual environments.

This photographed scene is part of a demo level from "The Life Stage: Virtual House," a building design simulator released in 1993 for the 3DO console.

Although the game has fallen into obscurity, it was notably ahead of its time for its use of photographic gameplay elements within an immersive 3D virtual space.

// Artwork by Sabato Visconti // www.sabatobox.com // @sabatobox on IG //
